reviewText: the grading has been so slow - I have taken several courses and this is the first one that I have had this problem with? The course itself is great but the grading is taking much longer than usual.
Too shallow.  Peer review every week is a waste of time.  I don't need this program.
having peers mark your work is slowing progress

I loved the way the instructor explained all the chapters, very communicative, good presentations and explanations. good exercises as well; the only uncomfortable thing happened at the end when the assignments I submitted were not checked, same for peer assignments, and I could not complete the course in due time. But overall, I found it great.
